	Ruined Temple - Golden Plates(Empty)
	
	There are 3 golden plates around the statue, each of them inside their own yellow circle, one of them is behind the 
statue, slightly to the right, the other 2 are in front of the statue, the one closer to the statue between the two, is right in 
front of it about 5 cm to the left, and the other one is slightly further away from the statue and much more to the left. They 
seem to make some kind of pattern, the one behind being connected to the statue directly and the one right in front of it too, 
only the one that's further away is connected to the next golden plate instead of the statue directly. As you inspect the 
closest golden plate to you, you see something engraved right in the middle of it, something is written there: 𐌔𐌄𐌂𐌏𐌍𐌃𐌀 𐌔𐌕𐌄𐌋𐌋𐌀 
𐌃𐌄 𐌖𐌉𐌍𐌂𐌖𐌋𐌏. You go to check the other plates as well to see if there's anything written on them as well, and the moment you 
clean the dust away from the next plate you see there is something written on it too: 𐌐𐌓𐌉𐌌𐌀 𐌔𐌕𐌄𐌋𐌋𐌀 𐌃𐌄 𐌖𐌉𐌍𐌂𐌖𐌋𐌏, last you check 
the plate behind the statue, and on this one it's engarved: 𐌗𐌋𐌉𐌀𐌓𐌉. What could it mean you wonder, maybe it means something...

-Investigate Statue. <Ruined Temple/ Statue>
-Check the strange drawings on the floor that connect the statue with the golden plates. <Ruined Temple/ Drawings>
-Place collected materials on the plates. <Ruined Temple/ Active Plates> (Only if the player has all materials: a goat's horn, 
fur and nail)
-Keep roaming around, maybe there’s something you’re not seeing, or maybe there isn’t, but you can’t be sure, can you? 
<Ruined Temple/ "Around">
-Leave temple. <Swamp entrance- After Temple>


	Ruined Temple - Golden Plates(Activation/active)
	
	You place the materials on top of the strange characters written in the plates. You place the goat horn on the plate that 
has written "𐌗𐌋𐌉𐌀𐌓𐌉", the fur on the plate that has written "𐌔𐌄𐌂𐌏𐌍𐌃𐌀 𐌔𐌕𐌄𐌋𐌋𐌀 𐌃𐌄 𐌖𐌉𐌍𐌂𐌖𐌋𐌏" on it and the nail on the last plate: 
"𐌓𐌉𐌌𐌀 𐌔𐌕𐌄𐌋𐌋𐌀 𐌃𐌄 𐌖𐌉𐌍𐌂𐌖𐌋𐌏". As soon as the nail touches the golden plate, all 3 materials you just placed burst into flames, the 
strange drawings start to glow, first the circles surrounding the plates and then it slowly extends along the lines, it looks as 
if they would get filled with some liquid. As you follow the light along the lines, rising your eyes little by little, you notice 
that the light reveals something written on the pedestal of the statue, it says: "The Password is : ARIES". Now, now... don't get 
so full of yourself, just because you got the password doesn't mean you know what to do with it!

-Investigate Statue. <Ruined Temple/ Statue> 
-Check writting on pedestal. <Ruined Temple/ Pedestal(after plates)>
-Check the strange drawings on the floor that connect the statue with the golden plates. <Ruined Temple/ Drawings>
